20annoying.%20I%20fall%20somewhere%20in%20the%20middle.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20I%20found%20the%20remote%20to%20be%20fine%20when%20using%20standard%20button%20presses%2C%20but%20there%20are%20still%20a%20few%20things%20I%20don't%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20issue%20is%20the%20scroll%20wheel%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20remote.%20This%20doubles%20as%20the%20enter%20key%20when%20you%20click%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20too%20easy%20to%20accidentally%20scroll%20when%20you're%20trying%20to%20select%20something.%20And%20when%20that%20happens%2C%20the%20TV%20automatically%20switches%20to%20motion%20control.%20There%20really%20should%20be%20an%20option%20in%20the%20menu%20to%20fully%20deactivate%20motion%20control%20for%20those%20who%20don't%20like%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20also%20disappointed%20that%20LG%20no%20longer%20includes%20dedicated%20input%20and%20mute%20buttons.%20To%20access%20the%20input%20selection%2C%20you%20need%20to%20hold%20the%20Home%20Hub%20button%20down.%20To%20mute%20the%20TV%2C%20you%20need%20to%20hold%20the%20volume%20down%20button.%20There%20is%20a%20new%20favorite%20button%20that%20you%20can%20assign%20a%20function%20to%2C%20which%20helps%20a%20bit%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20sure%20why%20we%20can't%20just%20have%20dedicated%20mute%20and%20input%20buttons.%20The%20remote%20also%20isn't%20backlit%2C%20which%20is%20a%20bummer.%20These%20are%20far%20from%20dealbreakers%2C%20but%20they%20are%20the%20kind%20of%20little%20quirks%20that%20stand%20out%20when%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20hardware%20feels%20so%20refined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259b4c244-c1bf-429f-ba03-4ce1028fba1a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Picture%20quality%5C%22%3EThe%20LG%20C6H%20delivers%20stunning%20OLED%20picture%20quality%20with%20a%20major%20boost%20in%20brightness%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221532%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20LG%20C6H%20OLED%20TV%20set%20up%20in%20our%20reviewer's%20home%20office%20with%20an%20image%20of%20zebras%20in%20the%20