y%20takes%20advantage%20of%20the%20C6H's%20capabilities.%20Colors%20dazzle%20in%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BAquaman%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20black%20levels%20are%20deep%20and%20inky%20in%20titles%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Matrix.%26quot%3B%20The%20burning%20church%20scene%20in%20%26quot%3B1917%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20great%20showcase%20for%20OLED%20tech's%20pixel-level%20contrast%2C%20and%20it%20demonstrates%20a%20level%20of%20precision%20and%20detail%20in%20shadows%20that%20no%20Mini%20LED%20TV%20can%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TV's%20impressive%20brightness%20is%20on%20full%20display%20in%20%26quot%3BMad%20Max%3A%20Fury%20Road%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20intense%20highlights%20that%20radiate%20off%20the%20screen.%20Some%20TVs%20struggle%20with%20highlights%20from%20the%20chrome%20car%20parts%20in%20this%20film%2C%20but%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126435850fp-20%26h%3Dc29ac1d85b6750f65d6c1a0982318c4c420e833af35bf967e0769ee73184c0d0%26postID%3D6a0770e5779c11677826115a%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Flg-c6h-oled-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0GRK913T8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EC6H%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0handles%20them%20with%20the%20intensity%20they%20deserve.%20Lightning%20bolts%20and%20explosions%20in%20the%20movie's%20memorable%20storm%20scene%20genuinely%20made%20me%20squint.%20This%20is%20stellar%20performance%20through%20and%20through%2C%20and%20a%20real%20home%20theater%20showcase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222189%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20an%20LG%20C6H%20OLED%20TV%20with%20an%20image%20of%20a%20sunrise%20in%20a%20canyon%20on%20screen.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a078555abc4e9d88574aa5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221642%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TV's%20image%20quality%20remains%20excellent%20from%20an%20angle%2C%20but%2