%3D6a0770e5779c11677826115a%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Flg-c6h-oled-4k-tv-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0GRK913T8%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EC6H%3C%2Fa%3E%20uses%20LG's%20webOS%20smart%20TV%20system.%20It's%20largely%20the%20same%20as%20last%20year's%20version%2C%20with%20some%20small%20tweaks.%20Setup%20is%20straightforward%2C%20but%20you'll%20need%20to%20create%20an%20LG%20account%20if%20you%20don't%20already%20have%20one%20to%20access%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20includes%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fbest-streaming-services%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20streaming%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20most%20people%20should%20be%20covered.%20However%2C%20it's%20still%20missing%20a%20few%20specialized%20apps%20available%20on%20other%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Criterion%20Channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20run%20into%20any%20major%20issues%20with%20general%20navigation%20through%20the%20home%20screen%20or%20streaming%20apps.%20But%20I%20do%20find%20moving%20through%20webOS's%20settings%20menus%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20slow%20compared%20to%20rival%20platforms%20like%20Google%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20visual%20design%20of%20webOS%20is%20decent%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20my%20favorite.%20By%20default%2C%20a%20large%20banner%20ad%20appears%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20homepage%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20row%20of%20your%20favorite%20apps.%20You%20also%20get%20various%20content%20recommendations%20and%20sponsored%20picks%2C%20along%20with%20a%20row%20of%20shopping%20recommendations%2C%20which%20I%20doubt%20anyone%20will%20find%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20ads%20and%20sponsored%20picks%20are%20par%20for%20the%20course%20on%20any%20smart%20TV%20interface%2C%20and%20LG%20does%20deserve%20credit%20for%20allowing%20you%20to%20disable%20the%20banner%20ad%20and%20recommendations%20from%20appearing%20on%20the%20home%20screen.%20This%20option%20is%20a%20bit%20buried%20in%20the%20menu%2C%20but%20it's%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20deactivating%20them%2C%20you%20simply%20get%20a%20placeholder%20banner%20image%20on%20top%20of%20your%20main%20row%20of%20apps%2C%20and%20that's%20it.%20I%20prefer%20this%20cleaner%20layout%2C%20but%20some%20people%20may%20find%20it%20a%20bit%20barebones.%20WebOS%20also%20supports%20multiple%20user%20profiles%2C%20so%20the%20home%20screen's%20recommendations%20and%20app%20selection%20can%20be%20personalized%20for%20each%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20gaming%20app%20menu%20on%20an%20LG%20C6H%20OLED%20TV.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0787a9ecd7cc1332bb0521%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECloud%20gaming%20services%20are%20available%20through%20the%20dedicated%20gaming%20page.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20webOS%20interface%20also%20includes%20a%20dedicated%20gaming%20section%20with%20access%20to%20several%20subscription-based%20cloud%20services.%20Most%20notably%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20Xbox%20or%20Nvidia%20GeForce%20Now%20apps%20to%20stream%20games%20to%20the%20TV%20without%20needing%20a%20console%20or%20PC.%20These%20apps%20are%20also%20available%20on%20TVs%20from%20some%20rivals%2C%20like%20Samsung%2C%20so%20it's%20nice%20that%20LG%20offers%20them%20as%20well.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELG%20has%20carried%20over%20various%20AI%20features%20it's%20introduced%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20including%20AI%20picture%20and%20audio%20modes%20that%20automatically%20optimize%20settings.%20There's%20also%20an%20AI%20Picture%20and%20Audio%20Wizard%20designed%20to%20personalize%20how%20these%20modes%20work%20by%20learning%20about%20your%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20unhappy%20with%20how%20any%20of%20the%20TV's%20built-in%20video%20and%20audio%20presets%20perform%2C%20these%20AI%20functions%20may%20be%20of%20interest.%20But%20as%20always%2C%20I%20highly%20recommend%20just%20using%20the%20TV's%20Filmmaker%20Mode%20and%20Standard%20audio%20mode%20to%20get%20the%20most%20accurate%20playback%2C%20and%20then%20tweaking%20things%20like%20brightness%20to%20your%20preference%20for%20your%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVoice%20search%20can%20be%20conducted%20by%20pressing%20the%20AI%20button%20on%20the%20remote%20or%20by%20enabling%20the%20TV's%20hands-free%20microphone%20and%20saying%20%26quot%3BHi%2C%20LG.%26quot%3B%20There's%20even%20a%20cool%20voice%20recognition%20feature%20that%20automatically%20switches%20the%20TV%20to%20different%20user%20profiles%20based%20on%20who's%20speaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20continue%20to%20find%20LG's%20voice%20assistant%20to%20be%20really%20inconsistent.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20results%20for%20voice%20queries%20were%20often%20slow%2C%20and%20the%20TV%20sometimes%20struggled%20to%20understand%20what%20I%20was%20saying%2C%20returning%20results%20for%20queries%20that%20were%20incorrect.%20I%20haven't%20had%20issues%20like%20this%20with%20other%20assistants%2C%20like%20Google's%20Gemini.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20ruins%20the%20experience%2C%20but%20webOS%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20C6H's%20weaker%20elements.%20It%20gets%20the%20job%20done%2C%20and%20I%20appreciate%20the%20customization%20options%2C%20but%20I'd%20still%20rather%20use%20a%20dedicated%20streaming%20device%20for%20day-to-day%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a6c1edbb-287e-4cef-9e3e-f8ade572c3c1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20LG%20C6H%20TV%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222037%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20LG%20C6H%20OLED%20TV%20in%20our%20reviewer's%20home%20office%2C%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20an%20island%20in%20the%20ocean.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.c