-strikes-in-gaza-targets-hamas-chief-11502432%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-carries-out-strikes-in-gaza-targets-hamas-chief-11502432%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Heathrow%20partnered%20with%20Salesforce%20to%20build%20a%20customer-service%20AI%20agent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22911%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Departures%20hall%20at%20London%20Heathrow%20Airport%20Terminal.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0378f195396a3b6e4178e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeathrow%20is%20the%20UK's%20busiest%20airport.%3Cp%3EHeathrow%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHeathrow's%20AI%20assistant%20handles%20traveler%20inquiries%20via%20WhatsApp%2C%20reducing%20the%20need%20for%20phone%20calls.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHeathrow%20leveraged%20its%20longtime%20partnership%20with%20Salesforce%20to%20create%20the%20tool%2C%20called%20Hallie.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHallie%20is%20set%20to%20expand%20to%20the%20airport's%20website%20and%20app%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2085%20million%20travelers%20passed%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-olympics-impact-heathrow-airport-raises-annual-passenger-forecasts-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHeathrow%20Airport%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202025.%20Amid%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%2C%20they%20had%20plenty%20of%20questions%3A%20How%20long%20will%20it%20take%20to%20get%20through%20security%3F%20Which%20Starbucks%20is%20closest%20to%20my%20departure%20gate%3F%20If%20my%20bag%20was%20left%20behind%20at%20security%2C%20how%20can%20I%20find%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20Burns%2C%20Heathrow's%20director%20of%20digital%2C%20e-commerce%2C%20and%20marketing%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20improve%20customer%20service%20at%20Europe's%20busiest%20airport%2C%20where%20demand%20keeps%20increasing.%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20grow%20capacity%2C%20we%20have%20to%20find%20a%20technology%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20To%20do%20that%2C%20Heathrow%20spent%20the%20past%20three%20years%20deepening%20its%20longtime%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-ai-executive-agency-problem-solving-more-important-learning-code-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESalesforce%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20started%20in%202009%2C%20Burns%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeathrow%20first%20implemented%20Salesforce's%20generative%20and%20agentic%20AI%20products%20in%202023%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20customer%20service%20applications.%20These%20initial%20tests%20led%20to%20the%20launch%20of%20Hallie%2C%20the%20airport's%20customer%20service%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-evolution-software-companies-develop-ai-agents-workforce-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20lives%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-competition-whatsapp-chatbot-battleground-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eon%20WhatsApp%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20answers%20nearly%20all%20traveler%20questions%20without%20human%20help%2C%20in%20March%202025%2C%20said%20Burns.%20Since%20finding%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20Hallie%20significantly%20reduced%20the%20number%20of%20customer%20calls%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20Heathrow%20is%20looking%20to%20further%20implement%20the%20tool%20on%20its%20website%20and%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomer%20service%20has%20been%20a%20popular%20use%20case%20for%20generative%20AI%20across%20industries%20since%20the%20debut%20of%20ChatGPT%20in%202022%2C%20said%20Gartner%20Research%20Vice%20President%20Bern%20Elliot.%20Elliot%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20a%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcustomer-service-support-chatbots%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecustomer%20contact%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20act%20as%20AI%20incubators%20because%20their%20return-on-investment%20metrics%20%E2%80%94%20time%20saved%2C%20agent%20call%20volume%2C%20response%20times%2C%20and%20response%20quality%2C%20among%20others%20%E2%80%94%20are%20clearly%20defined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20to%20connect%20very%20many%20dots%20to%20get%20from%20what%20you%20deployed%20to%20what%20is%20the%20measurable%20improvement%2C%26quot%3B%20Elliot%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20for%20a%20great%20starting%20place%20in%20your%20AI%20journey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20infusing%20AI%20into%20customer%20service%20systems%20isn't%20a%20straightforward%20process%2C%20said%20Elliot.%20AI%20systems%20should%20be%20trained%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-healthcare-companies-can-prepare-data-for-ai-assisted-management-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20company's%20most%20up-to-date%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20otherwise%2C%20large%20language%20models%20are%20more%20susceptible%20to%20giving%20incorrect%20responses.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20AI-ready%20data%20is%20a%20huge%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Elliot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurns%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20Salesforce's%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20solution%20engineering%2C%20Paul%20O'Sullivan%20%E2%80%94%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20about%20how%20Heathrow%20and%20Salesforce%20collaborated%20to%20navigate%20these%20data%20complexities%20and%20launch%20Hallie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FlQXCx%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Timeline%20of%20key%20events%20in%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20at%20Heathrow%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FlQXCx%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b0598f20-b88d-4cc0-a659-50306265469a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20tech%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Heathrow's%20initial%20Salesforce%20investments%20lacked%20AI%20capabilities%2C%20Burns%20said%20they%20were%20critical%20to%20creating%20a%20unified%20database%20that%20would%20later%20serve%20as%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20airport's%20customer%20service%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeathrow's%20relationship%20with%20Salesforce%20started%20in%20July%202009%20when%20it%20deployed%20Salesforce%20Service%20Cloud%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20helps%20customer%20service%20agents%20manage%20inquiries%20across%20multiple%20channels.%20By%20July%202021%2C%20Heathrow's%20customer%20and%20marketing%20data%20had%20been%20uploaded%20to%20Salesforce's%20real-time%20data%20platform%2C%20giving%20airport%20employees%20in%20customer%20service%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20e-commerce%20live%20views%20of%20passenger%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurns%20said%20Heathrow%20became%20an%20early%20adopter%20of%20Salesforce's%20generative%20AI%20capabilities%20in%202023%2C%20largely%20because%20of%20the%20airport's%20existing%20Salesforce%20product%20use.%20AI%20deployment%20began%20that%20January%20with%20two%20internal%20use%20cases%3A%20autonomously%20drafting%20replies%20to%20customer%20inquiries%20and%20creating%20case%20wrapups%2C%20the%20summaries%20that%20customer%20service%20agents%20prepare%20after%20helping%20someone.%20These%20two%20tests%20fed%20more%20information%20into%20Heathrow's%20database%2C%20helping%20to%20continuously%20refine%20the%20quality%20of%20AI-drafted%20responses%2C%20Burns%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20late%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-salesforce-struggles-agentforce-flagship-ai-agent-wars-benioff-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESalesforce's%20Agentforce%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20software%20company's%20autonomous%20AI%20platform%20that%20can%20complete%20customer%20service%2C%20sales%2C%20and%20marketing%20tasks%20automatically%20%E2%80%94%20was%20deployed%20in%20the%20airport's%20contact%20center%20to%20assist%20human%20agents%20with%20two%20specific%20tasks%3A%20Writing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-ai-chatbots-online-robot-chat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eresponses%20to%20customer%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2C%20after%20a%20case%20was%20resolved%2C%20generating%20a%20summary.%20Previously%2C%20agents%20had%20to%20type%20out%20every%20response%20and%20case%20summary%2C%20Burns%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Heathrow%20worked%20closely%20with%20O'Sullivan%20and%20his%20team%20of%20UK-based%20engineers%20to%20test%20and%20improve%20the%20airport's%20AI%20capabilities%20before%20Hallie's%20launch.%20Salesforce%20has%20regularly%20met%20with%20Heathrow's%20team%20since%20their%20partnership%20began%20in%202009%2C%20with%20in-person%20visits%20about%20once%20per%20quarter%20and%20regular%20virtual%20catch-ups%20every%20other%20week%2C%20O'Sullivan%20said.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20their%20meetings%20have%20focused%20on%20observing%20contact%20agents'%20workflows%20and%20identifying%20pain%20points%20where%20AI%20could%20be%20applied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Sullivan%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20is%20critical%20for%20executive%20leadership%2C%20product%20managers%2C%20engineers%2C%20and%20representatives%20from%20security%2C%20data%2C%20and%20cloud%20teams%20to%20be%20on%20the%20same%20page%20before%20deploying%20tools%20like%20Agentforce%2C%20since%20internal%20databases%20could%20be%20outdated%20and%20make%20the%20technology%20less%20useful.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20these%20agents%20need%20to%20be%20exactly%20like%20you%20and%20I%2C%20and%20how%20we%20work%2C%20because%20we're%20constantly%20learning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Heathrow%2C%20Agentforce%20pulls%20from%20the%20airport's%20database%20of%20500%20articles%20outlining%20processes.%20However%2C%20some%20of%20the%20policies%20took%20several%20months%20to%20gather%2C%20update%2C%20and%20implement%2C%20Burns%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202024%2C%20Heathrow%20added%20more%20of%20its%20internal%20data%20to%20Salesforce's%20data%20platform%2C%20enabling%20the%20airport%20to%20provide%20customers%20with%20real-time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftext-yourself-flight-number-code-life-hack-iphone-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflight-tracking%20data%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeathrow's%20unified%20data%20foundation%2C%20which%20brought%20together%20Heathrow%20customer%20data%2C%20airport%20maps%2C%20flight%20statuses%2C%20and%20advances%20in%20generative%20AI%2C%20led%20to%20the%20March%202025%20launch%20of%20Heathrow's%20AI%20agent%20Hallie.%20On%20WhatsApp%2C%20travelers%20can%20ask%20Hallie%20questions%20about%20upcoming%20flights%2C%20how%20to%20find%20specific%20airport%20amenities%20and%20terminals%2C%20and%20the%20length%20of%20the%20security%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220de7ba2-2fe8-4505-8c41-070c2d2b662f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20outcome%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%20launch%20of%20Hallie%2C%2070%25%20of%20customer%20inquiries%20were%20handled%20by%20phone%2C%20said%20Burns.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20bot's%20agentic%20capabilities%2C%20by%20March%202026%2C%20phone%20calls%20accounted%20for%2010%25%20of%20traveler%20inquiries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20this%20year%2C%20Hallie%20will%20expand%20beyond%20WhatsApp%20so%20customers%20can%20access%20the%20tool%20on%20Heathrow's%20website%20and%20app%2C%20Burns%20added.%20The%20airport%20is%20also%20considering%20future%20rollouts%20for%20Hallie%2C%20like%20at%20kiosks%20throughout%20its%20terminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Hallie's%20guardrails%20are%20limited%3A%20it%20only%20scrapes%20data%20from%20Heathrow's%20website%20and%20internal%20database%2C%20Burns%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20aren't%20letting%20the%20agent%20go%20out%20into%20the%20open%20web%20and%20pull%20out%20other%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20This%20decision%20somewhat%20limits%20the%20AI%20agent's%20outputs%2C%20as%20it%20cannot%20yet%20handle%20personalized%20questions%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%20can%20I%20pick%20up%20my%20checked%20bags%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurns%20said%20it%20was%20important%20for%20Hallie%20to%20provide%20accurate%20responses%2C%20and%20added%20that%20external%20sources%20could%20have%20inaccurate%20or%20out-of-date%20information.%20Looking%20forward%2C%20Heathrow%20plans%20to%20add%20more%20functionality%20to%20Hallie%20so%20passengers%20can%20use%20the%20tool%20on%20platforms%20beyond%20WhatsApp%2C%20Burns%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheathrow-salesforce-ai-chatbot-customer-service-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778870017000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0378eb58810e27922acd5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheathrow-salesforce-ai-chatbot-customer-service-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Heathrow%20and%20Salesforce%20launched%20AI%20assistant%20Hallie%20to%20manage%20customer%20inquiries%2C%20boosting%20efficiency%20at%20the%20UK's%20busiest%20airport.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20Kell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump's%20Beijing%20Visit%20Ends%20With%20'Bin%20Order'%20For%20Chinese-Issued%20Items%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22While%20Trump%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20kept%20up%20a%20cordial%20front%20on%20camera%2C%20relations%20between%20American%20and%20Chinese%20press%20and%20security%20teams%20were%20far%20more%20strained%20behind%20the%20scenes.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778869354000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2