%2Fa%3E%2C%20Singapore%20Airlines%20was%20named%20the%20world's%20best%20international%20airline%20by%20Travel%20%2B%20Leisure%20in%202025.%20It%20also%20won%20the%20title%20of%20best%20airline%20in%20Asia%20at%20last%20year's%20Skytrax%20World%20Airline%20Awards%2C%20considered%20the%20Oscars%20of%20the%20aviation%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Singapore%20Airlines%20is%20famous%20for%20its%20luxurious%20suites%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-airlines-first-class-suite-double-bed-is-worlds-best-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst-class%20cabins%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20could%20only%20afford%20an%20economy%20ticket.%20But%20my%20experience%20was%20still%20far%20better%20than%20my%20recent%20trips%20on%20US%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20impressed%20with%20Singapore%20Airlines%20before%20my%20flight%20even%20began.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screengrab%20of%20Singapore%20Airlines%20seat%20selection%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eea66969253ccddf9b24cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221116%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20travel%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-better-japan-but-grateful-for-life-united-states-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapan%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20friend's%20wedding%20in%20Sydney%20and%20booked%20an%20economy%20ticket%20on%20Singapore%20Airlines.%20There%20are%20four%20different%20tiers%20of%20economy%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0lite%2C%20value%2C%20standard%2C%20and%20flexi%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20only%20standard%20was%20available%20on%20my%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trip%2C%20which%20included%20a%20layover%20in%20Singapore%2C%20cost%20%24814.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20booking%20my%20Singapore%20Airlines%20ticket%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20that%20I%20could%20select%20seats%20on%20both%20of%20my%20flights%20for%20free.%20I%20could%20even%20choose%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BForward%20Zone%26quot%3B%20seats%2C%20which%20are%20closer%20to%20the%20doors%20and%20allow%20you%20to%20disembark%20first%20from%20economy.%20This%20felt%20like%20a%20great%20option%20since%20my%20layover%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-changi-airport-best-place-for-layover-australian-living-us-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChangi%20Airport%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20I%20got%20to%20pick%20the%20window%20seat%20(my%20favorite)%20for%20both%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20also%20surprised%20by%20the%20airline's%20generous%20weight%20limit%20for%20checked%20bags.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Singapore%20Airlines%20check-in%20desk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eea6e969253ccddf9b24d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221340%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20notorious%20overpacker.%20If%20there%20were%20a%20gold%20medal%20for%20shuffling%20items%20from%20your%20checked%20bag%20to%20carry-on%20to%20meet%20the%2050-pound%20limit%20of%20most%20US%20airlines%2C%20I%20would%20be%20the%20Simone%20Biles%20of%20the%20sport.%20It's%20a%20natural%20gift%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20even%20have%20to%20train!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20when%20the%20Singapore%20Airlines%20attendant%20told%20me%20I%20needed%20to%20put%20%3Cem%3Emore%3C%2Fem%3E%20stuff%20in%20my%20checked%20bag%2C%20not%20less.%20She%20informed%20me%20that%20the%20weight%20limit%20for%20checked%20bags%20in%20economy%20is%2030%20kilograms%2C%20or%20about%2066%20pounds.%20If%20you%20fly%20Singapore%20Airlines%20on%20economy%20lite%20or%20value%2C%20the%20limit%20is%2025%20kilograms%2C%20or%20about%2055%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20able%20to%20unload%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcarry-on-bags-checked-luggage-size-charge-airlines-planes-travel-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoverstuffed%20carry-on%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20gallivant%20around%20duty-free%20was%20an%20unexpected%20pre-flight%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20boarding%20my%20flight%2C%20I%20grabbed%20a%20pair%20of%20headphones%20by%20the%20plane's%20entrance.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Singapore%20Airlines%20headphones%20basket%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb029963d72727e198c344%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20small%20detail%2C%20but%20I%20appreciated%20that%20I%20could%20immediately%20sit%20and%20start%20watching%20a%20movie%20without%20waiting%20for%20an%20attendant%20to%20pass%20out%20the%20headphones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20chair%20was%20far%20more%20spacious%20than%20what%20I've%20come%20to%20expect%20from%20US%20airlines.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Singapore%20Airlines%20seats%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb02b1b8b41a9673fc37dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who's%20only%20flown%20economy%2C%20I've%20become%20all%20too%20accustomed%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouthwest-airlines-new-premium-seats-economy-class-less-space-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreasingly%20shrinking%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20was%20flying%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20href