0the%20seat%20between%20us%2C%20we%20easily%20slid%20both%20of%20our%20backpacks%20under%20the%20middle%20seat%20and%20enjoyed%20the%20extra%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20seat%20in%20front%20of%20me%20had%20helpful%20buttons%20and%20compartments.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Singapore%20Airlines%20screen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb02c363d72727e198c34e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20left%20corner%20of%20my%20screen%20were%20buttons%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20overhead%20light%20and%20call%20the%20attendant%2C%20plus%20an%20outlet%20to%20charge%20my%20phone.%20Under%20the%20right%20corner%20was%20a%20stand-alone%20drink%20holder.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20shelf%20under%20my%20screen%2C%20where%20I%20stored%20my%20headphones%20when%20I%20wasn't%20watching%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20appreciated%20the%20four%20separate%20pockets%20in%20front%20of%20my%20seat.%20I%20could%20easily%20store%20my%20phone%2C%20book%2C%20magazine%2C%20charger%2C%20and%20water%20bottle%20in%20all%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20had%20access%20to%20an%20extensive%20entertainment%20selection.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Singapore%20Airlines%20movie%20selection%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb0312b8b41a9673fc37f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singaporeair.com%2Fen_UK%2Fus%2Fflying-withus%2Fentertainment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Singapore%20Airlines%20offers%20more%20than%201%2C900%20on-demand%20options%20via%20its%20KrisWorld%20in-flight%20entertainment%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20everything%20from%20%26quot%3BWicked%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-substance-ending-explained-demi-moore-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Substance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20I%20didn't%20feel%20brave%20enough%20to%20watch%20on%20a%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETV%20options%20included%20food%20shows%2C%20kids'%20programs%2C%20and%20classics%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BLaw%20%26amp%3B%20Order%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Golden%20Girls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20takeoff%2C%20flight%20attendants%20passed%20out%20hot%20towels%20to%20everyone%20on%20board.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Singapore%20Airlines%20hand%20towel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb033a63d72727e198c362%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20custom%2C%20known%20in%20Japanese%20as%20%26quot%3Boshibori%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20a%20longtime%20signature%20of%20the%20Singapore%20Airlines%20brand.%20Each%20towel%20is%20perfumed%20with%20the%20airline's%20%26quot%3BBatik%20Flora%26quot%3B%20scent%2C%20which%20combines%20the%20floral%20notes%20of%20various%20flowers%20that%20are%20native%20to%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20I%20had%20given%20my%20hands%20a%20refreshing%20cleanse%2C%20an%20attendant%20returned%20to%20retrieve%20the%20towel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWithin%2020%20minutes%20of%20takeoff%2C%20we%20were%20given%20our%20first%20drink%20and%20snack.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Singapore%20Airlines%20cupholder%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb036663d72727e198c36b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWho%20hasn't%20chugged%20their%20little%20drink%20on%20a%20plane%20because%20there%20wasn't%20enough%20space%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20stand-alone%20cupholder%2C%20I%20could%20leisurely%20sip%20on%20my%20complimentary%20glass%20of%20white%20wine%20as%20I%20snacked%20on%20the%20peas-and-crackers%20snack%20and%20read%20my%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20came%20the%20dinner%20service.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20airplane%20meal%20on%20the%20tray%20table%2C%20comprising%20chicken%20and%20vegetables%2C%20a%20prawn%20noodle%20salad%2C%20cheese%20and%20crackers%2C%20a%20bread%20roll%2C%20and%20a%20bottle%20of%20water.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb037a69253ccddf9ad1ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20tray%20included%20an%20entr%C3%A9e%20of%20chicken%20or%20fish%20(the%20vegetarian%20meals%20had%20already%20been%20served)%2C%20bread%2C%20a%20small%20noodle%20salad%2C%20Australian%20cheese%20and%20crackers%2C%20and%20a%20mini%20water%20bottle.%20I%20was%20surprised%20it%20came%20with%20metal%20cutlery%20rather%20than%20the%20plastic%20or%20wood%20I'm%20used%20to%20seeing%20in%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20with%20the%20salad%2C%20which%20featured%20vermicelli%20noodles%20and%20shrimp%20cooked%20far%20more%20delicately%20than%20expected%20for%20an%20in-flight%20meal.%20The%20shrimp%20were%20plump%20and%20fresh%2C%20pairing%20well%20with%20the%20light%2C%20tangy%20dressing%20that%20covered%20each%20noodle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20opted%20for%20the%20chicken%20entr%C3%A9e%2C%20which%20was%20solid.%20The%20meat%20was%20tender%20and%20covered%20in%20sauce%2C%20while%20the%20potatoes%20were%20well-cooked%20but%20under-seasoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20exactly%20gourmet%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20huge%20upgrade%20from%20the%20undercooked%20pasta%20and%20rubbery%20meat%20I've%20had%20on%20many%20long-haul%20flights%20with%20US%20airlines.%20(And%20I'll%20never%20forget%20the%20tortilla%20filled%20with%20a%20cut-up%20hot%20dog.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EShortly%20after%20we'd%20settled%20into%20dinner%2C%20attendants%20offered%20us%20an%20ice%20cream%20sandwich%20for%20dessert.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holding%20a%20Superslice%20vanilla%20fudge%20brownie.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb038d63d72727e198c372%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20delicious%20vanilla%20fudge%20brownie%20was%20a%20highlight%20of%20the%20flight.%20It%20featured%20a%20chocolate%20crunch%20on%20the%20bottom%20that%20satisfyingly%20snapped%20with%20every%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAn%20hour%20before%20landing%2C%20we%20were%20given%20a%20hot%20snack.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holding%20a%20sandwich%20filled%20with%20melted%20cheese.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb039e63d72727e198c379%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20offered%20a%20choice%20between%20a%20sandwich%20with%20sweet%20potato%20and%20cheese%20or%20sweet%20chili%20chicken.%20I%20chose%20the%20latter%2C%20which%20was%20fine.%20I%20couldn't%20taste%20the%20sweet%20chili%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20nice%2C%20warm%20snack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20I%20had%20a%20great%20first%20experience%20on%20Singapore%20Airlines.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225374%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Singapore%20Airlines%20plane%20parked%20on%20the%20tarmac%20at%20Singapore%20Changi%20Airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6696805e8893442a5156f55d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223582%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Singapore%20Airlines%20Airbus%20A380.%3Cp%3EROSLAN%20RAHMAN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20economy%20is%20economy.%20Still%2C%20the%20experience%20has%20become%20increasingly%20uncomfortable%20as%20US%20carriers%20shrink%20their%20seats%20and%20add%20more%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20flying%20on%20Singapore%20Airlines%20felt%20like%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air.%20From%20the%20hot%20towel%20and%20spacious%20seats%20to%20the%20decent%20in-flight%20entertainment%20and%20food%20options%2C%20my%20nine-hour%20flight%20seemed%20to%20fly%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20see%20why%20Singapore%20Airlines%20consistently%20ranks%20among%20the%20top%20in%20the%20world.%20I%20can't%20wait%20to%20fly%20on%20one%20of%20its%20planes%20again.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-airlines-economy-flight-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778865254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eeaf3ab8b41a9673fc8d5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-airlines-economy-flight-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Singapore%20Airlines%20is%20consistently%20named%20among%20the%20best%20airlines%20in%20the%20world.%20Even%20in%20economy%2C%20the%20seats%20are%20spacious%20and%20the%20food%20is%20decent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22akonstantinides%40businessinsider.com%20(Anneta%20Konstantinides)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%