cludes%20with%20her%20term's%20end%2C%20opening%20the%20door%20for%20new%20representation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ryan%20Cohen's%20eBay%20stunt%20earned%20him%20%24168K.%20His%20top%20sale%20was%20a%20Halo%20Master%20Chief%20statue.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22GameStop%20CEO%20Ryan%20Cohen%20is%20pictured%20with%20his%20sold%20eBay%20listings.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07223eabc4e9d88574a5e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGameStop%20CEO%20Ryan%20Cohen%20earned%20over%20%24168K%20from%20selling%20personal%20items%20on%20eBay.%3Cp%3EGameStop%3B%20Screenshot%20via%20eBay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGameStop%20CEO%20Ryan%20Cohen's%20eBay%20listings%20have%20ended.%20He%20earned%20%24168%2C421.39.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20top-earning%20item%20was%20a%20large%20statue%20from%20%26quot%3BHalo%202%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20sold%20for%20%2415%2C100.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGameStop%20offered%20%2455.5%20billion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-big-short-michael-burry-sold-gamestop-ryan-cohen-ebay-2026-5%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efor%20eBay%3C%2Fa%3E%20(which%20eBay%20rejected).%20Cohen's%20haul%20accounts%20for%20about%200.0003%25%20of%20the%20proposed%20price.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20Cohen%20pulled%20in%20a%20hefty%20sum%20from%20his%20baseball%20cards%2C%20merch%2C%20and%20gaming%20collectibles%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20eBay%20listing%20stunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20of%20GameStop%20posted%20a%20collection%20of%20items%20for%20resale%20after%20announcing%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-ceos-awkward-interview-after-billion-ebay-offer-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunsolicited%20bid%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20eBay%2C%20which%20the%20company%20has%20since%20rejected.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20selling%20stuff%20on%20eBay%20to%20pay%20for%20eBay%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fryancohen%2Fstatus%2F2052077872135704802%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20week%20later%2C%20the%20listings%20have%20closed%2C%20and%20the%20items%20have%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen's%20total%20haul%3A%20%24168%2C421.39.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20highest-earning%20item%20was%20a%20large%20Master%20Chief%20statue%20from%20%26quot%3BHalo%202.%26quot%3B%20The%20statue%20was%20listed%20for%20local%20pickup%20in%20Grapevine%2C%20Texas%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0where%20GameStop%20is%20headquartered%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20sold%20for%20%2415%2C100.%20It%20received%20105%20bids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222730%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20%26quot%3BHalo%202%20Master%20Chief%20Statue%26quot%3B%20was%20Ryan%20Cohen's%20top-earning%20listing.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07313594eb4c909fb2cddc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221288%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERyan%20Cohen's%20highest-earning%20item%20was%20a%20statue%20from%20%26quot%3BHalo%202.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20via%20eBay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20top%20earners%20include%20two%20store%20signs%20from%20shuttered%20GameStop%20locations%20(%2414%2C921%2C%20105%20bids)%20and%20two%20collectible%20statues%20from%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-park-creators-matt-parker-trey-stone-net-worth-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESouth%20Park%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20(%2413%2C400%2C%2087%20bids).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20also%20sold%20a%20collectible%20card%20picturing%20Donald%20Trump's%202016%20swearing%20in%2C%20which%20was%20graded%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcard-collecting-pokemon-kpop-photocard-pro-assessor-value-psa-grading-2026-4%23speed-grading-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20PSA%2010%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20card%20sold%20for%20%246%2C470%20with%2044%20bids.%20The%20buyer%20seemed%20pleased%2C%20leaving%20Cohen%20a%20positive%20review%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmooth%20transaction%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3Bexcellent%20communication.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lowest-earning%20item%20was%20a%201995%20baseball%20card%20of%20Vladimir%20Guerrero.%20It%20pulled%20in%20%241%2C694%20and%2069%20bids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20haul%20is%20a%20drop%20in%20the%20bucket%20of%20GameStop's%20%2455.5%20billion%20bid%2C%20which%20Cohen%20has%20said%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bhalf%20cash%2C%20half%20stock.%26quot%3B%20The%20%24168%2C421.39%20total%20is%20about%200.0003%25%20of%20the%20deal%20total%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20publicity%20stunt%20nature%20of%20the%20item%20listings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen's%20profile%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-ryan-cohen-claims-ebay-account-suspended-listings-remain-active-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebriefly%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20eBay%20after%20its%20system%20flagged%20high%20price%20points.%20EBay%20restored%20the%20account%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20not%20before%20Cohen%20posted%20about%20it%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20casualty%20of%20Cohen's%20initial%20vision%20for%20the%20listings%20was%20his%20socks%2C%20which%20at%20one%20point%20had%20attracted%20bidding%20over%20%2414%2C000.%20Used%20underwear%20and%20socks%20violate%20eBay's%20used%20clothes%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222744%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20GameStop%20signs%20were%20the%20second-highest%20earning%20listing.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07319cabc4e9d88574a6a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20second-highest-earning%20item%20from%20Ryan%20Cohen's%20eBay%20sale%20was%20two%20signs%20from%20shuttered%20GameStop%20stores.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20via%20eBay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20now%20faces%20an%20even%20steeper%20uphill%20climb%20toward%20his%20goal%20of%20becoming%20CEO%20of%20a%20combined%20eBay%20and%20GameStop%20entity.%20EBay%20earlier%20this%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Febay-rejects-ryan-cohen-gamestop-55-billion-takeover-offer-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erejected%20GameStop's%20offer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20its%20chairman%2C%20Paul%20Pressler%2C%20called%20the%20proposal%20%26quot%3Bneither%20credible%20nor%20attractive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20rejection%2C%20Cohen%20responded%20with%20an%20email%20to%20Pressler%2C%20writing%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20dismiss%20a%20%24125%20per%20share%20proposal%20without%20engaging%20on%20its%20substance%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bshareholders%20deserve%20the%20opportunity%20to%20evaluate%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fe11c447d-6ee7-46a0-a593-894076c3f36c%3Fsyn-25a6b1a6%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFT%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Piers%20Morgan%2C%20Cohen%20signaled%20he%20wasn't%20done%20fighting%20for%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20job%20to%20do%20the%20best%20for%20shareholders%20and%20engage%20on%20this%2C%20and%20if%20they%20don't%20then%20we'll%20do%20whatever%20we%20need%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-ceo-ryan-cohen-ebay-listings-earnings-halo-trump-card-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778863950000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07223eabc4e9d88574a5e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busines