re%20not%20actively%20typing%2C%20you%20rest%20the%20elbow%20of%20your%20non-mouse-using%20arm%20onto%20your%20desk%3F%20Me%20too!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20do%20you%20find%20that%20sometimes%2C%20that%20elbow%20gets%20a%20little%20sore%20from%20sitting%20there%20on%20a%20hard%20desk%20surface%20for%20potentially%20hours%20a%20day%3F%20Me%20too!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Body%20horror%20storytime%3A%20Several%20years%20ago%2C%20my%20elbow%20suddenly%20swelled%20up%20and%20got%20hot%20and%20painful%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20few%20hours%3B%20I%20got%20woozy%20and%20feverish%2C%20requiring%20a%20trip%20to%20urgent%20care%20for%20an%20antibiotic%20shot.%20An%20orthopedist%20told%20me%20the%20next%20day%20it%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-sitting-is-killing-you-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecase%20of%20bursitis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20appear%20rapidly%20in%20the%20elbow%20if%20banged%20or%20just%20from%20resting%20it%20on%20your%20desk%20for%20hours%20a%20day.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20ever%20find%20yourself%20wanting%20to%20put%20something%20soft%20%E2%80%94%20the%20end%20of%20your%20sweatshirt%2C%20a%20folded-up%20winter%20hat%2C%20the%20edge%20of%20your%20Neoprene%20laptop%20case%20%E2%80%94%20under%20where%20your%20elbow%20goes%20to%20give%20it%20some%20comfort%3F%20Buddy%2C%20you%20know%20what%20I'm%20about%20to%20say%20(me%20too).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20if%20I%20told%20you%20that%20there%20is%20an%20item%20you%20can%20use%2C%20a%20special%20one%20made%20exactly%20for%20this%20purpose%2C%20that%20will%20relieve%20that%20specific%20pain%20and%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20the%20suffering%20and%20misery%20of%20your%20tortured%20existence%3F%20And%20that%20this%20one%20magical%20object%20will%20break%20you%20free%20of%20the%20prison%20of%20your%20corporeal%20suffering%20and%20help%20you%20ascend%20to%20a%20plane%20of%20pure%20light%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-