iatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fscientists-used-ai-and-high-tech-scans-in-perus-nazca-desert-the-result-was-303-hidden-geoglyphs%2Famp_articleshow%2F131122660.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fscientists-used-ai-and-high-tech-scans-in-perus-nazca-desert-the-result-was-303-hidden-geoglyphs%2Famp_articleshow%2F131122660.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hundreds%20of%20Russian%20Shaheds%20are%20descending%20on%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20daytime%2C%20signaling%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20warfare%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Ukrainian%20man%20crouches%20as%20he%20holds%20a%20P1-Sun%20interceptor%20drone%20and%20prepares%20it%20for%20launch.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a06b4f694eb4c909fb2cbb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20prepares%20a%20P1-Sun%20interceptor%20drone%20ahead%20of%20incoming%20Shahed%20attacks.%3Cp%3EPierre%20Crom%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EInstead%20of%20attacking%20with%20Shaheds%20at%20night%2C%20Russia%20is%20now%20trying%20dayslong%20strike%20campaigns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20week%2C%20Ukraine%20said%20it%20was%20attacked%20with%20over%201%2C500%20drones%20and%2050%20missiles%20for%20two%20straight%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETwo%20analysts%20studying%20Shahed%20warfare%20said%20it's%20an%20early%20sign%20of%20a%20new%20tactic%20aimed%20at%20wearing%20Ukraine%20down.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Ukrainian%20cities%2C%20the%20last%20two%20days%20have%20been%20a%20near-constant%20barrage%20of%20drones%20and%20missile%20strikes%2C%20culminating%20in%20Russia's%20largest%20and%20most%20unrelenting%20long-range%20attack%20in%20the%20war%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20another%20major%20episode%20in%20a%20new%20style%20of%20Russian%20drone%20warfare%20emerging%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20the%20Kremlin%20previously%20relied%20on%20attacking%20Ukraine%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-russia-now-us-one-style-drone-reshaping-moden-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edelta-wing%20Shaheds%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20night%20%E2%80%94%20when%20they're%20harder%20to%20spot%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20starting%20to%20deploy%20them%20in%20extended%20windows%20that%20last%20long%20into%20the%20day%2C%20forcing%20Ukrainians%20to%20shelter%20for%20hours%20or%20take%20their%20chances%20to%20go%20about%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzelenskyy-russia-earned-billion-iran-war-oil-trade-deficit-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20his%20country%20came%20under%20siege%20from%201%2C567%20drones%20and%2056%20missiles%20from%20Wednesday%20to%20Thursday%2C%20describing%20the%20assault%20as%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20and%20virtually%20continuous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20look%20up%20at%20a%20large%20black%20drone%20on%20display%20in%20front%20of%20a%20blue%20and%20white%20church%20with%20a%20gold%20top%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fdff6aba7ef34b41f36631%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussia%20has%20been%20deploying%20its%20own%20version%20of%20the%20Iranian-designed%20Shahed.%20Ukraine%20showcased%20a%20Shahed%20136%20at%20an%20exhibition%20of%20Russian%20weapons%20in%20November.%3Cp%3EGenya%20SAVILOV%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week's%20bombardment%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bprime%20example%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20trend%2C%20said%20Igor%20Anokhin%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20senior%20analyst%20who%20sifts%20through%20data%20on%20Russia's%20Shahed%20strikes%20for%20the%20Washington-based%20think%20tank%20Institute%20for%20Science%20and%20International%20Security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20salvo%20marks%20the%20fifth%20time%20that%20the%20Kremlin%20has%20used%20sustained%20strike%20periods%20this%20year%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20call%20this%20a%20fully%20established%20pattern%20yet%2C%20but%20it%20is%20clearly%20becoming%20a%20new%20operational%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20Anokhin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20of%20these%20prolonged%20attacks%20was%20in%20late%20March%2C%20when%20Russia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-oleksandr-syrskyi-russia-1000-shahed-per-day-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaunched%20nearly%201%2C000%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20Ukraine%20over%2024%20hours%2C%20Anokhin%20added.%20Another%20notable%20example%20occurred%20in%20mid-April%2C%20when%20continuous%20drone%20and%20missile%20attacks%20lasted%20for%2032%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20against%20a%20daily%20average%20of%20143%20to%20219%20drones%20this%20year%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20month%2C%20according%20to%20Anokhin's%20analyses%20of%20Ukrainian%20and%20open-source%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20often%20also%20targets%20Ukraine's%20electrical%20grid%2C%20forcing%20millions%20to%20go%20through%20the%20winter%20without%20heat%20in%20a%20campaign%20aimed%20at%20reducing%20the%20population's%20will%20to%20resist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f2077c6-76a6-48e9-b038-5d4fb10d8f33%5C%22%3EWhy%20daytime%20strikes%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEnduring%20an%20extended%20onslaught%20is%20exhausting%2C%20as%20Business%20Insider's%20Jake%20Epstein%20and%20Rob%20Leslie%20found%20during%20the%20recent%20attack.%20They%20took%20cover%20for%20hours%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-daytime-drone-attack-nighttime-missile-barrage-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKyiv%20bomb%20shelter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20waiting%20sleeplessly%20through%20the%20night%20as%20explosions%20rattled%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShahed%20attacks%20are%20so%20frequent%20that%20they've%20already%20become%20an%20accepted%20part%20of%20life%20for%20Ukrainian%20civilians.%20Anokhin%20said%20that's%20the%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20goal%20is%20psychological%20pressure%20and%20economic%20terror%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BKeeping%20Ukrainian%20cities%20on%20high%20alert%20for%20many%20hours%2C%20disrupting%20civilian%20life%2C%20and%20targeting%20energy%20and%20critical%20infrastructure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heightened%20pressure%20also%20puts%20Ukraine's%20multi-layered%20air%20defense%20network%20to%20the%20test.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-interceptor-drones-air-defense-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETo%20counter%20aerial%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ukrainian%20forces%20deploy%20a%20mix%20of%20mobile%20machine-gun%20crews%2C%20interceptor%20drones%2C%20electronic%20warfare%2C%20and%20high-end%20defensive%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mobile%20fire%20group%20of%20the%20208th%20Kherson%20Anti-Aircraft%20Missile%20Brigade%20demonstrates%20coordinated%20actions%20and%20available%20weapons%2C%20including%20a%20heavy%20machine%20gun%20mounted%20on%20a%20turret%2C%20a%20man-portable%20air%20defense%20system%20(MANPADS)%2C%20and%20small%20arms%2C%20in%20the%20Mykolaiv%20region%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20on%20March%2030%2C%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fc79fe3cfefc31768d682d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETo%20counter%20Shahed%20attacks%2C%20Ukrainian%20forces%20deploy%20machine-gun%20crews%20who%20stay%20mobile%20with%20civilian%20trucks.%3Cp%3ENina%20Liashonok%2FUkrinform%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-launched-largest-drone-attack-ever-russia-ports-uavs-report-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esheer%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-launched-largest-drone-attack-ever-russia-ports-uavs-report-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evolume%20of%20threats%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20Russia%20strains%20that%20system.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20forcing%20Ukraine%20to%20fire%20more%20rare%2C%20expensive%20interceptors%20to%20destroy%20a%20cheap%20drone%2C%20making%20room%20for%20ballistic%20missiles%20to%20find%20their%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20employed%20that%20tactic%20this%20week%3A%20After%20hours%20of%20drone%20attacks%2C%20missiles%20began%20pounding%20Kyiv%20on%20Wednesday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20said%20air%20defenses%20destroyed%20at%20least%2093%25%20of%20Russia's%20drones%20during%20the%20attack%2C%20but%20that%20only%2073%25%20of%20Russia's%20missiles%20were%20downed.%20As%20of%20Thursday%20evening%2C%2024%20people%20were%20confirmed%20dead%2C%20and%20another%2048%20were%20injured%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20Shahed%20costs%20less%20than%20%2450%2C000%20to%20produce%20and%20carries%20up%20to%20110%20pounds%20of%20explosive%20that%20strikes%20with%20a%20shrapnel-laden%20blast%20powerful%20enough%20to%20cripple%20buildings%20and%20kill%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225355%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rescue%20workers%20navigate%20debris%20of%20a%20collapsed%20building%20in%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a06b3b9ecd7cc1332baff02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223570%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20building%20in%20Kyiv%20partially%20collapsed%20during%20this%20week's%20prolonged%20window%20of%20strikes.%3Cp%3EDanylo%20Dubchak%2FFrontliner%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFederico%20Borsari%2C%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20European%20Policy%20Analysis%20who%20focuses%20on%20drone%20warfare%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20daytime%20attacks%20can%20also%20serve%20a%20secondary%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-found-western-parts-russian-decoy-drone-fools-air-defenses-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussia's%20decoy%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20equipped%20with%20electro-optical%20sensors%2C%20which%20can%20scout%20the%20battlefield%20while%20soaking%20up%20Ukrainian%20air%20defense%20munitions%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20targets%20are%20typically%20mobile%20fire%20groups%2C%20ground-based%20air%20defense%20launchers%2C%20and%20other%20high-value%20military%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20Borsari%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20daytime%20drone%20waves%20can%20pinpoint%20high-value%20targets%20for%20follow-on%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnokhin's%20analysis%20found%20that%20in%20April%2C%2066%25%20of%20Russia's%20launched%20one-way%20drones%20were%20Shaheds%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20were%20decoys%20or%20other%20types%20of%20strike%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9dffc3f-5101-4a8c-8b03-52f9c7c02215%5C%22%3EThe%20production%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20attacked%20in%20longer%20windows%20before%2C%20but%20not%20at%20this%20scale.%20Both%20Borsari%20and%20Anokhin%20said%20a%20key%20change%20is%20Russia's%20growing%20ability%20to%20deploy%20more%20drones%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20ideal%20to%20destroy%20production%20in%20Alabuga%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anokhin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Yelabuga%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Alabuga%2C%20in%20Russia's%20Tatarstan%20region%2C%20is%20home%20to%20the%20Kremlin's%20main%20factory%20for%20Shaheds%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhich%20has%20come%20under%20intense%20global%20scrutiny%20as%20a%20vital%20component%20of%20the%20Russian%20war%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20working%20quickly%20to%20ramp%20up%20production%20there%2C%20even%20as%20Ukraine%20sends%20its%20own%20long-range%20drones%20to%20attack%20the%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20May%209%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.svoboda.org%2Fa%2Fplyus-340-gektarov-kak-rasshirilasj-za-god-oez-alabuga%2F33753251.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERadio%20Free%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20satellite%20images%20showed%20new%20facilities%20and%20hangars%20at%20the%20site%2C%20expanding%20the%20campus%20by%20340%20hectares%20while%20more%20construction%20was%20starting%20on%20another%20450%20hectares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20Anokhin%2C%20Russia's%20Shahed%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Edeployment%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehas%20grown%20steadily%20since%20early%202025%20and%20now%20accounts%20for%20a%20larger%20share%20of%20drone%20strikes%2C%20rising%20from%2059%25%20of%20total%20launches%20in%20the%20fall%20of%20last%20year%20to%2064%25%20this%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FsxgmN%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FsxgmN%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20ragtag%20air%20defense%20network%2C%20however%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20working.%20Anokhin's%20analysis%20shows%20that%20while%20nearly%20a%20third%20of%20Russia's%20Shaheds%20were%20hitting%20targets%20in%20the%20fall%2C%20that%20proportion%20has%20fallen%20sharply%20to%20around%2014%25%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FTWzOQ%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FTWzOQ%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20has%20been%20emphasizing%20cheaper%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdemand-surges-intercept-drones-can-defeat-threats-like-iran-shaheds-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einterceptor%20drones.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ukraine's%20air%20force%20estimated%20in%20February%20that%20about%2030%25%20of%20Russian%20drones%20are%20downed%20by%20these%20inexpensive%20remote%20systems%2C%20though%20the%20reported%20proportion%20has%20risen%20to%2070%25%20in%20some%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorsari%20and%20Anokhin%20said%20separately%20that%20they%20believe%20Russia's%20extended%20daytime%20drone%20waves%20will%20become%20a%20more%20permanent%20fixture%20in%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20the%20Russian%20targeting%20strategy%20is%20bearing%20fruit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Borsari.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-daytime-drone-strikes-night-shahed-ukraine-war-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778862329000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a06b8e994eb4c909fb2cbce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-daytime-drone-strikes-night-shahed-ukraine-war-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Typical%20nighttime%20drone%20waves%20are%20giving%20way%20to%20massive%20attacks%20that%20last%20days%2C%20with%20the%20most%20recent%20bombardment%20involving%20over%201%2C500%20drones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20bitcoin%20traders%20are%20suddenly%20obsessed%20with%20a%20forgotten%20crypto%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Z%20bucks%20coin%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a07522394eb4c909fb2cf5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBackyardProduction%2FiStock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EZcash%2C%20a%20cryptocurrency%20launched%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20is%20suddenly%20surging%20in%20popularity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECrypto%20pros%20say%20investors%20are%20drawn%20to%20the%20token%20due%20to%20its%20emphasis%20on%20privacy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInterest%20has%20been%20rising%20for%20months%2C%20ever%20since%20a%20post%20on%20X%20described%20Zcash%20as%20%26quot%3Binsurance%20against%20Bitcoin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20decade-old%20digital%20token%20is%20suddenly%20all%20the%20rage%20in%20crypto%20circles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZEC%2C%20a%20token%20launched%20in%202016%20using%20the%20Zcash%20blockchain%20protocol%2C%20has%20seen%20its%20price%20surge%2050%25%20in%20a%20month%2C%20even%20as%20bitcoin%20struggles%20to%20break%20out%20of%20its%20slump.%20The%20apex%20crypto%20is%20up%20about%206%25%20in%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20token%20is%20relatively%20unknown%20outside%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzcash-price-zec-gemini-mining-what-you-need-to-know-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20prominent%20early%20adopters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20prized%20the%20crypto%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaw-enforcement-problems-with-monero-zcash-dash-cryptocurrencies-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemphasis%20on%20privacy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20received%20little%20attention%20for%20years%20before%20unexpectedly%20surging%20late%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20care%20about%20ZCash%20because%20it%20represents%20one%20of%20the%20few%20major%20crypto%20networks%20built%20around%20financial%20privacy%20as%20a%20core%20feature%20rather%20than%20an%20afterthought%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20Daniel%20Reis%20Faria%2C%20CEO%20of%20AI-focused%20asset%20management%20firm%20Zerostack.%20%26quot%3BAs%20surveillance%20across%20both%20traditional%20finance%20and%20blockchain%20increases%2C%20there's%20renewed%20interest%20in%20assets%20that%20preserve%20optionality%20and%20confidentiality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReis%20Faria%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Zcash%20appeals%20not%20just%20to%20crypto%20traders%20but%20also%20to%20institutions%20because%20it%20protects%20the%20details%20of%20their%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Zcash%20offers%20that%20bitcoin%20doesn't%20is%20shielded%20transaction%20capability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%20%26quot%3BBitcoin%20is%20often%20misunderstood%20as%20anonymous%2C%20but%20in%20reality%20it's%20highly%20transparent%20and%20traceable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBobby%20Ong%2C%20CEO%20and%20Co-founder%20of%20CoinGecko%2C%20traces%20the%20surge%20in%20Zcash%20interest%20to%20an%20October%201%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fnaval%2Fstatus%2F1973254136394293708%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20tech%20entrepreneur%20Naval%20Ravikant%20who%20stated%20simply%20%26quot%3BBitcoin%20is%20insurance%20against%20fiat.%20Zcash%20is%20insurance%20against%20Bitcoin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20post%2C%20Zcash%20was%20trading%20at%20%2474%20per%20coin.%20Since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20risen%20to%20a%20peak%20of%20more%20than%20%24600%20per%20token.%20Ong%20noted%20that%20several%20other%20catalysts%20have%20followed%20since%20Ravikant%20shared%20stoked%20fresh%20interest%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20momentum%20was%20followed%20by%20major%20allocations%20from%20Multicoin%20Capital%20and%20Arthur%20Hayes%2C%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20first%20US%20spot%20Zcash%20ETF%2C%20and%20the%20emergence%20of%20digital%20asset%20treasury%20company%20(DATCo)%20Cypherpunk%20Technologies%20accumulating%20ZEC%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20reinforced%20the%20view%20that%20privacy%20coins%20were%20moving%20back%20into%20the%20mainstream%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defining%20narrative%20seems%20to%20be%20that%20in%20a%20world%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-secrets-sensitive-legal-risk-confidentiality-lawsuit-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eincreasingly%20driven%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20AI%20and%20powerful%20tools%20that%20could%20jeopardize%20the%20security%20offered%20by%20cryptography%2C%20the%20need%20for%20privacy%20is%20increasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Jefferies%20predicted%20that%20the%20rise%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-price-prediction-quantum-computing-risk-cryptography-jefferies-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equantum%20computing%20will%20be%20a%20top%20threat%20to%20bitcoin%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20future.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20man%20who%20had%20been%20locked%20out%20of%20his%20crypto%20wallet%20for%2011%20years%20claimed%20this%20week%20that%20he%20used%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20to%20brute%20force%20his%20way%20back%20in%2C%20getting%20the%20AI%20bot%20to%20test%203.5%20trillion%20passwords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeightened%20anonymity%20and%20privacy%20is%20the%20central%20part%20of%20what's%20driving%20the%20appeal%20of%20Zcash%20right%20now%2C%20causing%20traders%20to%20embrace%20the%20crypto%20that%2C%20until%20recently%2C%20seemed%20largely%20forgotten.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Bohbot%2C%20chief%20growth%20officer%20at%20digital%20asset%20investment%20firm%20RockawayX%2C%20said%20she%20isn't%20surprised%20by%20the%20recent%20Zcash%20rush.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrivacy%20coins%20have%20become%20more%20interesting%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20LLMs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20giving%20models%20more%20personal%20data%20than%20they've%20given%20any%20technology%20before%2C%20and%20over%20time%20they'll%20want%20to%20protect%20their%20data%20privacy%20more.%20Money%20and%20LLM%20usage%20are%20where%20that%20demand%20lands%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzcash-price-what-is-zec-bitcoin-btc-crypto-privacy-tokens-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778862290000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzcash-price-what-is-zec-bitcoin-btc-crypto-privacy-tokens-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20token%20launched%20in%202016%20is%20suddenly%20in%20the%20limelight%20in%20crypto%20circles.%20Zcash%20has%20surged%2C%20far%20outpacing%20gains%20in%20bitcoin%20in%20the%20last%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seth%20Rogen%20about%20his%20film%20'Tangles'%20at%20Cannes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778862032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131122527%2Cimgsize-56478.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fseth-rogen-opens-up-about-tangles-premiere-at-cannes-film-festival-i-was-crying-a-lot-throughout-the-entire-thing%2Farticleshow%2F131122490.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131122490.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESeth%20Rogen's%20animated%20film%20'Tangles%2C'%20a%20poignant%20story%20about%20Alzheimer's%20based%20on%20Sarah%20Leavitt's%20memoir%2C%20premiered%20at%20Cannes%2C%20leaving%20the%20actor%20deeply%20emotional.%20Witnessing%20the%20decade-long%20project%20r