%20TECH%20team%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWriting%20this%20and%20sharing%20this%20news%20is%20harder%20than%20I%20expected.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAfter%20seven-plus%20years%20together%2C%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20leave%20Paramount.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EBut%20before%20I%20do%2C%20what%20I%20most%20want%20to%20say%20%E2%80%94%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20really%20matters%20%E2%80%94%20is%20thank%20you.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThank%20you%20for%20showing%20up%2C%20every%20single%20day%2C%20through%20conditions%20that%20would%20have%20broken%20lesser%20teams.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThank%20you%20for%3A%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20late%20nights%20and%20the%20early%20mornings.%20For%20the%20problems%20you%20solved%20that%20no%20one%20ever%20saw%2C%20and%20the%20ones%20you%20fixed%20that%20kept%20the%20whole%20thing%20running%20and%20got%20none%20of%20the%20credit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBeing%20relentlessly%20focused%20on%20the%20complete%20technology%20and%20service%20experience%20for%20our%20internal%20and%20external%20customers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEvery%20integration%20meeting%2C%20every%20migration%2C%20every%20system%20failure%20at%202%20a.m.%20that%20somehow%20you%20turned%20around%20by%20dawn.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENot%20flinching%20when%20COVID%20hit%20%E2%80%94%20keeping%20our%20people%20safe%20and%20our%20voice%20on%20the%20air.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProtecting%20the%20company%20diligently%20while%20building%20modern%2C%20AI-first%20cybersecurity%20capabilities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDoing%20whatever%20was%20needed%20to%20get%20that%20show%20on%20the%20air%2C%20that%20production%20asset%20delivered%2C%20or%20that%20promo%20to%20pop.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStreaming%20all%20of%20those%20live%20events%20at%20record-breaking%20scale%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20Super%20Bowl%20in%202019%2C%20on%20infrastructure%20that%20was%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20exists%20today.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERebuilding%20our%20entire%20media%20supply%20chain%2C%20ad%20tech%20ecosystem%2C%20licensing%20solutions%2C%20and%20more%20into%20genuinely%20best-in-class%20technology%20and%20operations%20platforms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEmbracing%20the%20AI%20opportunity%20early%20and%20bringing%20others%20along%20to%20advance%20our%20capabilities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGiving%20us%20one%20final%20win%20together%20%E2%80%94%20Oracle%20Fusion%20in%20just%2015%20months%2C%20a%20feat%20almost%20no%20organization%20at%20our%20scale%20has%20pulled%20off.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Csection%3EWhile%20delivering%20on%20all%20of%20this%20for%20Paramount%2C%20you%20also%20kept%20innovation%2C%20technical%20excellence%2C%20and%20user%20experience%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20our%20efforts.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20saw%20all%20of%20it.%20Every%20bit%20of%20it.%20You%20set%20the%20company%20up%20for%20real%20success%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EBut%20what%20I%20am%20most%20grateful%20for%20is%20not%20the%20accomplishments%20%E2%80%94%20as%20remarkable%20as%20they%20are.%20It%20is%20the%20people.%20The%20culture%20of%20this%20team.%20The%20way%20you%20solve%20hard%20problems%20together.%20The%20way%20you%20hold%20each%20other%20up%20through%20wave%20after%20wave%20of%20change%20and%20uncertainty.%20The%20way%20you%20have%20consistently%20shown%20what%20is%20possible%20when%20talented%2C%20good%20people%20commit%20to%20something.%20That%20is%20what%20I%20will%20carry%20with%20me.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20challenges%20coming%20down%20the%20road%20are%20real.%20The%20pace%20of%20change%20in%20technology%2C%20in%20AI%2C%20in%20how%20content%20is%20made%20and%20distributed%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20only%20accelerating.%20The%20work%20ahead%20will%20be%20demanding.%20None%20of%20that%20is%20new%20to%20this%20team.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20want%20to%20be%20clear%20about%20something%3A%20you%20are%20exceptionally%20well-positioned%20for%20everything%20ahead%20of%20you.%20The%20foundation%20we%20built%20together%20%E2%80%94%20the%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20platforms%2C%20the%20operational%20discipline%2C%20the%20AI%20capabilities%20we%20put%20in%20place%20%E2%80%94%20is%20not%20just%20solid.%20It%20is%20a%20genuine%20competitive%20advantage.%20You%20have%20done%20the%20hard%20work.%20You%20know%20how%20to%20do%20this.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAs%20for%20me%2C%20I%20am%20heading%20back%20to%20my%20Silicon%20Valley%20tech%20roots%20to%20advance%20some%20ideas%20on%20enterprise%20AI.%20More%20to%20come%20on%20that%20at%20a%20later%20time.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20I%20remain%20energized%20and%20excited%20about%20the%20possibilities%20emerging%20in%20this%20AI%20revolution.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3ESeven%20years.%20What%20a%20journey.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EIt%20has%20been%20the%20honor%20of%20a%20lifetime%20to%20work%20alongside%20every%20one%20of%20you.%20And%20I%20will%20be%20cheering%20you%20on%20as%20I%20dive%20into%20what's%20next.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20am%20here%20through%20the%20end%20of%20May%20and%20hope%20to%20see%20many%20of%20you%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%20to%20say%20farewell.%20You%20can%20always%20find%20me%20online%20%E2%80%94%20please%20stay%20in%20touch.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EStay%20Scrappy!%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EPhil%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-skydance-tech-chief-leaving-read-the-memo-david-ellison-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778861733000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a074543abc4e9d88574a773%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-skydance-tech-chief-leaving-read-the-memo-david-ellison-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paramount's%20chief%20tech%20officer%20is%20stepping%20down%20during%20David%20Ellison's%20digital%20transformation.%20Read%20the%20memo%20to%20employees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jfaris%40businessinsider.com%20(James%20Faris)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Drake%20reveals%20his%20father%20is%20battling%20cancer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778861082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131122186%2Cimgsize-119940.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fdrake-reveals-his-father-is-battling-cancer-in-new-iceman-song-make-them-cry%2Farticleshow%2F131122186.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131122186.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERapper%20Drake%20has%20revealed%20his%20father%2C%20Dennis%20Graham%2C%20is%20battling%20cancer%20in%20his%20new%20song%20'Make%20Them%20Cry'.%20The%20emotional%20track%20details%20Drake's%20personal%20struggles%20and%20family%20responsibilities.%20Graham%2C%20a%20musician%20himself%2C%20has%20since%20posted%20a%20supportive%20message%20on%20social%20media%2C%20prompting%20an%20outpouring%20of%20well%20wishes%20from%20fans%20for%20his%20health%20journey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taylor%20Swift%20collaborator%20Jack%20Antonoff%20tells%20people%20who%20are%20making%20AI%20art%20to%20'drive%20right%20off%20that%20cliff'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jack%20Antonoff%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0722ab94eb4c909fb2cd31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222267%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJack%20Antonoff%20has%20written%20for%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20Kendrick%20Lamar.%3Cp%3EGary%20Gershoff%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJack%20Antonoff%20defended%20traditional%20songwriting%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bholy%20process%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20open%20letter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAntonoff%20denounced%20AI-generated%20music%20as%20a%20way%20to%20fake%20making%20art.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20isn't%20the%20first%20artist%20to%20condemn%20the%20use%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20the%20arts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20has%20seeped%20into%20many%20industries%2C%20and%20one%20hit%20songwriter%20has%20a%20strong%20opinion%20on%20its%20place%20in%20the%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20Antonoff%2C%20the%2042-year-old%20singer-songwriter%20who%20has%20worked%20with%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20Kendrick%20Lamar%2C%20published%20a%20letter%20Thursday%20in%20defense%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bancient%20ritual%26quot%3B%20of%20making%20music.%20In%20an%20Instagram%20post%2C%20Antonoff%20slammed%20those%20looking%20for%20a%20way%20to%20make%20songwriting%20easier%20or%20quicker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20to%20write%20music%20anymore%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20record%20it%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20bring%20the%20band%20out%20and%20play%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Antonoff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI-generated%20content%20has%20made%20its%20way%20into%20fields%20from%20academia%20to%20illustration%20to%20music.%20Some%20companies%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-innovating-music-tools-artists-labels-creators-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeveloping%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20automate%20tasks%20in%20the%20music%20industry%2C%20such%20as%20mastering%20a%20track.%20There%20are%20also%20AI%20assistants%20specifically%20designed%20to%20write%20songs%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftilly-norwood-ai-music-video-jobs-hollywood-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20pop%20stars%3C%2Fa%3E%20dropping%20singles%20on%20streaming%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAntonoff%20is%20having%20none%20of%20it.%20He%20condemned%20the%C2%A0idea%20of%20using%20tech%20to%C2%A0optimize%20the%20%26quot%3Bholy%20process%26quot%3B%20of%20writing%2C%20recording%2C%20and%20performing%20music.%20He%20said%20he%20spoke%20on%20behalf%20of%20himself%2C%20his%20band%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Beveryone%20I%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20called%20out%20%26quot%3Bbad%20actors%26quot%3B%20who%20he%20said%20would%20eventually%20be%20revealed%20by%20the%20slop%20they%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20to%20everyone%20who%20is%20gassed%20up%20about%20the%20new%20ways%20you%20can%20fake%20making%20art%2C%20by%20all%20means%20drive%20right%20off%20that%20cliff%2C%26quot%3B%20Antonoff%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20genuinely%20happy%20to%20see%20you%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20not%20the%20first%20in%20the%20music%20industry%20to%20come%20for%20AI-generated%20music.%20Label%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-the-music-industry-is-changing-its-tune-on-ai-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUniversal%20Music%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20gone%20toe-to-toe%20with%20AI%20multiple%20times%20to%20get%20music%20made%20to%20look%20and%20sound%20like%20its%20artists%20taken%20down%20from%20streaming%20platforms.%20Artist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjason-derulo-ai-music-not-good-enough-threat-artists-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJason%20Derulo%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20also%20said%20AI%20music%20lacks%20soul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAntonoff%20said%20that%20the%20new%20musicians%20he%20knows%20aren't%20interested%20in%20AI-generated%20music.%20He%20was%20blunt%20in%20what%20he%20thinks%20about%20the%20people%20creating%20%26quot%3Bslop%26quot%3B%20that's%20hitting%20streaming%20services%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGodless%20whores%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjack-antonoff-slams-ai-in-music-defends-songwriting-process-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778861041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0722b9abc4e9d88574a5e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjack-antonoff-slams-ai-in-music-defends-songwriting-process-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jack%20Antonoff%2C%20a%20songwriter%20for%20Taylor%20Swift%2C%20criticized%20AI%20in%20music%2C%20defending%20traditional%20creative%20processes%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bholy%26quot%3B%20artistic%20ritual.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20husband%20and%20I%20got%20a%20roommate%20to%20save%20money.%20It%20worked%20surprisingly%20well%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20we'd%20never%20do%20it%20again.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222501%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Jordan%20Mautner%20and%20husband%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a05eb2cecd7cc1332bafb7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221879%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20about%20a%20year%2C%20we%20had%20a%20positive%20experience%20renting%20out%20a%20room%20in%20our%20home.%20Eventually%2C%20we%20realized%20the%20arrangement%20wasn't%20sustainable%20for%20us.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Mautner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20we%20got%20married%2C%20we%20rented%20out%20our%20spare%20bedroom%20to%20save%20money.%20At%20first%2C%20it%20worked%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEventually%2C%20we%20started%20to%20feel%20uncomfortable%20in%20our%20own%20home%20and%20too%20reliant%20on%20this%20extra%20income.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20grateful%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-buying-first-starter-home-wrong-choice-los-angeles-regrets-2026-5%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erebuilt%20our%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20we%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20roommate%20and%20don't%20want%20one%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20getting%20married%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20the%20idea%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-host-rental-spare-bedroom-side-hustle-income-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erent%20out%20the%20spare%20room%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20our%20two-bedroom%20apartment%20to%20help%20rebuild%20our%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'd%20just%20spent%20a%20lot%20on%20our%20wedding%20and%20honeymoon%2C%20and%20reducing%20our%20biggest%20living%20expense%20meant%20we'd%20have%20more%20money%20in%20our%20pockets%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20spare%20bedroom%20is%20at%20the%20far%20end%20of%20our%20apartment%2C%20far%20enough%20away%20to%20maintain%20our%20privacy%2C%20making%20it%20an%20ideal%20space%20to%20rent.%20Plus%2C%20a%20friend%20of%20a%20friend%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20place%20to%20live.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20a%20roommate%20felt%20like%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20and%20a%20great%20way%20for%20us%20to%20get%20back%20on%20track%20financially%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20for%20a%20while%2C%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fca7fd7c-58f9-4bfb-b64a-46f6e6d50c4a%5C%22%3EAt%20first%2C%20our%20new%20living%20arrangement%20worked%20well%20and%20provided%20a%20huge%20financial%20relief%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dog%20on%20couch%20in%20living%20room%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a05e9b094eb4c909fb2c7ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERenting%20out%20our%20spare%20room%20seemed%20like%20a%20great%20way%20for%20us%20to%20quickly%20rebuild%20our%20savings.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Mautner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20few%20months%2C%20things%20went%20really%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20new%20roommate%20was%20in%20the%20hospitality%20industry%20and%20primarily%20worked%20at%20night%2C%20whereas%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20worked%20during%20the%20day.%20Since%20everyone%20had%20different%20routines%2C%20we%20weren't%20stepping%20on%20each%20other's%20toes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20nice%20to%20share%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsplit-household-chores-based-on-strengths-interests-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehousehold%20responsibilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20keeping%20the%20apartment%20clean%20became%20second%20nature%20with%20a%20roommate.%20When%20someone%20else%20would%20be%20using%20the%20kitchen%20or%20bathroom%20after%20you%2C%20you%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20it's%20in%20good%20shape%20for%20the%20next%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20perk%20of%20our%20new%20living%20situation%20was%20the%20financial%20relief%3A%20one-third%20of%20our%20bills%20were%20covered.%20With%20this%2C%20our%20savings%20began%20to%20grow%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20started%20planning%20some%20vacations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20a%20two-week-long%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-time-visiting-sicily-mistakes-do-differently-next-trip-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eroad%20trip%20around%20Sicily%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20were%20able%20to%20visit%20my%20husband's%20family%20in%20Argentina.%20We%20also%20have%20a%20dog%2C%20and%20our%20roommate%20loved%20dogs%2C%20so%20when%20we%20were%20away%2C%20they%20would%20take%20care%20of%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20my%20house%20was%20tidy%2C%20we%20had%20a%20live-in%20dog%20sitter%2C%20and%20our%20savings%20were%20growing.%20What%20could%20go%20wrong%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b5b763d-1f38-4397-980d-b6a0103d0b39%5C%22%3EOver%20time%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20stopped%20feeling%20comfortable%20in%20our%20own%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20dog%2C%20smiling%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a05e987abc4e9d88574a0e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlthough%20there%20were%20perks%20to%20having%20someone%20live%20with%20us%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20it%20was%20holding%20us%20back.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Mautner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20say%20that%20one%20particular%20incident%20caused%20us%20to%20second-guess%20having%20a%20roommate.%20Rather%2C%20over%20time%2C%20we%20realized%20this%20couldn't%20be%20a%20long-term%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20newlyweds%2C%20and%20although%20taking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-romantic-destinations-according-to-frequent-traveler-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eromantic%20vacations%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20dreamy%2C%20we%20started%20to%20crave%20our%20privacy%20at%20home.%20Oftentimes%2C%20we%20found%20ourselves%20not%20wanting%20to%20use%20the%20common%20spaces%20in%20the%20house%20and%20trying%20to%20make%20as%20little%20noise%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshare-house-with-strangers-surprising-benefits-downsides-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehaving%20a%20roommate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20our%20favorite%20activities%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20long%20day%20was%20curling%20up%20on%20our%20couch%20to%20watch%20a%20movie.%20Now%2C%20we%20found%20ourselves%20doing%20this%20in%20our%20bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we'd%20hear%20my%20roommate's%20key%20in%20the%20lock%20during%20mealtime%2C%20we'd%20sometimes%20scurry%20into%20our%20room%20with%20our%20dinner%20plates%20just%20to%20have%20quiet%20time%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20couldn't%20enjoy%20the%20beautiful%20home%20we%20had%20worked%20so%20hard%20to%20make%20our%20own%2C%20and%20feeling%20uncomfortable%20in%20it%20was%20affecting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsex-tips-decades-married-couple-intimacy-fun-lingerie-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintimacy%20in%20our%20marriage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c188b524-b1fb-41bf-b40d-349539ca3735%5C%22%3EEventually%2C%20the%20financial%20benefits%20just%20weren't%20worth%20it%20anymore%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20months%2C%20we'd%20also%20begun%20to%20rely%20too%20much%20on%20the%20savings%20from%20renting%20the%20spare%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20more%20money%20to%20save%20each%20month%20also%20meant%20having%20more%20to%20potentially%20spend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20definitely%20traveling%20more%20than%20we%20could%20realistically%20afford%20on%20our%20own%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sign%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Flifestyle-creep%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elifestyle%20creep%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20financial%20relief%20was%20always%20meant%20to%20be%20temporary%3B%20we%20couldn't%20get%20too%20attached%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20also%20started%20to%20cause%20tension%20and%20arguments%20between%20my%20husband%20and%20me.%20I%20was%20ready%20for%20the%20roommate%20to%20leave%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20wanted%20them%20to%20stay%20a%20bit%20longer%20so%20our%20finances%20could%20get%20back%20on%20track%20after%20all%20the%20big%20spending%20on%20our%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20after%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20give%20our%20roommate%20two%20months'%20notice%20to%20leave.%20This%20gave%20them%20time%20to%20find%20something%2C%20and%20gave%20us%20time%20to%20prepare%20financially%20to%20go%20roommate-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20just%20the%20two%20of%20us%20for%20about%20six%20months%20now%2C%20and%20we%20definitely%20feel%20freer%20in%20our%20own%20home%20%E2%80%94%20able%20to%20watch%20long%20movies%20on%20the%20couch%20and%20leave%20a%20dish%20or%20two%20in%20the%20sink%2C%20guilt-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20still%20adjusting%20to%20working%20with%20a%20much%20tighter%20budget%2C%20but%20at%20least%20it's%20a%20more%20sustainable%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20we'd%20like%20to%20avoid%20having%20a%20roommate%20again%2C%20I%20would%20still%20recommend%20this%20to%20couples%20looking%20for%20extra%20cash%20flow%20as%20long%20as%20they%20weigh%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20set%20a%20clear%20deadline%20with%20their%20partner%20for%20how%20long%20the%20arrangement%20will%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-rented-spare-room-save-money-mistakes-pros-cons-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778860921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a06095194eb4c909fb2c8eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-rented-spare-room-save-money-mistakes-pros-cons-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20extra%20income%20from%20renting%20our%20extra%20room%20and%20getting%20a%20roommate%20helped%20us%20financially%2C%20but%20it%20began%20affecting%20our%20marriage%20and%20spending%20habits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Mautner)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Keneeshaa%20Francis%20quits%20social%20media%20after%20emotional%20videos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778860653000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131122098%2Cimgsize-89258.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fkeneeshaa-francis-quits-social-media-after-emotional-videos-on-ravi-mohan-aarti-ravi-separation-ive-left-chennai-i-give-up%2Farticleshow%2F131121599.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofin